narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: In this course, you learn how to evaluate H NMR spectra, use Scifinder, and continue using all the skills learned in the first orgo lab class.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The strength are the fact that each lab is very engaging and ties into the lecture course in some way. However, it can be a little repetitive, which isn't necessarily bad.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend this course if you've taken the first part of this lab and enjoyed it, since it basically continues with the same theme of synthetic chemistry.
